options.text: Don't worry, I'm not going to cause trouble.

0979eb92-5b4a-47ad-8696-174d78faf6f9.title: <player>
0979eb92-5b4a-47ad-8696-174d78faf6f9.text:
No, you're just imagining it. Perhaps you've been up
here in the sun for too long?

f9dc5e26-7fa2-45a8-9b18-70d0dcc1e893.title: Guard
f9dc5e26-7fa2-45a8-9b18-70d0dcc1e893.text: So who am I talking to?

80d2515f-8a5d-4151-af19-f6d788de90b4.title: <player>
80d2515f-8a5d-4151-af19-f6d788de90b4.text:
Oh dear, you've started talking to yourself. That's a
common sign that you're going mad!

c3eb75f2-d7a4-4e33-b9f6-6ac93f51b236.title: Guard
c3eb75f2-d7a4-4e33-b9f6-6ac93f51b236.text: But... but... you're standing right there...

args: Maybe you should leave him alone now.

34e9b596-561d-4734-a5aa-d259de0e0d71.title: Guard
34e9b596-561d-4734-a5aa-d259de0e0d71.text:
Mighty? You look like another of those silly adventurers
who thinks they're the bee's knees just because they've
done a few lousy quests!

4ceac9e7-3098-42cc-b63a-79b8e8aae984.title: <player>
4ceac9e7-3098-42cc-b63a-79b8e8aae984.text:
Well it sounds better than sitting on this rooftop all day
looking at trees!

cea27a10-f726-4df2-8c35-83918d04ef3b.title: Guard
cea27a10-f726-4df2-8c35-83918d04ef3b.text:
I'll have you know it's a very important job guarding
this jail!

e929726b-8988-4a77-9cbc-55c0a594b20a.title: Guard
e929726b-8988-4a77-9cbc-55c0a594b20a.text:
If anyone comes sneaking in here to mess around with
the prisoners, the lads downstairs will make mincemeat
of them, and I'll be here to pick them off if they try to
escape.

f955d203-7b4a-4350-83d9-a801a9b12542.title: <player>
f955d203-7b4a-4350-83d9-a801a9b12542.text:
You mean people aren't meant to be able to shoot the
prisoners in the cells?

c87f2c73-8a8d-498e-8fbe-90024e97af4f.title: <player>
c87f2c73-8a8d-498e-8fbe-90024e97af4f.text: Okay, it's been nice talking to you.

39527f01-c50b-45c1-90e8-d5a8e220ebf4.title: <player>
39527f01-c50b-45c1-90e8-d5a8e220ebf4.text: Don't worry, I'm not going to cause trouble.

80b78357-5991-4f17-8619-e4d516e30e57.title: Guard
80b78357-5991-4f17-8619-e4d516e30e57.text: But you shouldn't be here - be off with you!
